videos.description: Johnathan Williams gets the feed underneath the basket and goes up strong getting the foul and the bucket to fall for one more.
videos.headline: Gonzaga's Williams collects bucket and-1

videos.description: Zach Norvell Jr. pokes the ball away and leads Corey Kispert ahead on the fast break, who draws the foul and drops the bucket.
videos.headline: Norvell Jr. steal leads to Kispert and-1 just before half

videos.description: Killian Tillie tells Trae Berhow to get his shot out of there with an emphatic block.
videos.headline: Tillie volleyball spikes a block

videos.description: Killian Tillie brings down the defensive board and then goes from end-to-end for the layup.
videos.headline: Tillie drives coast-to-coast for easy bucket
